root: ^Did you find something that could help me...?
^That's just a bunch of leaves and stuff...
^Heh... having all these autumn things in me makes me think of how much I love this season...
^Autumn leaves, Halloween, witches, werewolves, black cats...
^I'd really like to be a cat...
^Yeah! Look at me! I really like this!
^I guess it just took a bit of thinking to really figure out who I wanted to be.
^...And a bit of help from a friend.
^Well, I'm glad you were able to figure yourself out! And I'm glad I could help!
